{"tid":1180774,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"COYS！我地熱刺今晚又準備捧盃 稱霸歐洲","createTime":"2019-06-01T05:58:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-01T20:50:43.000Z","uid":11258,"like":17,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"03f280029bd829bb80efeae645a51204453d6df5","tid":1180774,"uid":11258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T05:58:47.000Z","msg":"[quote]<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://bit.ly/2L2ISp1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2L2ISp1&h=6c46b7af&s={SIZE}\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">C</span></strong></span><span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">OME</span></span> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">O</span></strong></span><span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">N</span></span> <span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>Y</strong></span></span><span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">OU</span></span> <span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>S</strong></span></span><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\">HITS</span></span><img src=\"https://bit.ly/2L2ISp1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2L2ISp1&h=6c46b7af&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n[center]<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n岩岩起完新球場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n作為熱迷梗係踴躍捐錢比熱刺起個博物館收藏我地熱刺既獎盃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QtAiFwv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQtAiFwv.png&h=056c92f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有近年最高榮耀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ygy0TR6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYgy0TR6.png&h=ec8eb15c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n急不及待好想今晚玩玩了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地託特納姆熱刺迷個個揸林寶堅尼<br />\n買返個貼下先 今晚捧盃揸出去巡遊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z6wedTM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ6wedTM.png&h=4ef8ae7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n已經淘左屬於我熱既盃今晚著住禾熱波衫捧盃自拍上IG FB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pOkbgGX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpOkbgGX.png&h=06c23556&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n賤種熱狗可以死返出去發你個春秋大夢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4df312b1d3ffc3143fdd345ee1c8e201201da0eb","tid":1180774,"uid":11258,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T06:01:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f3fyu3r.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff3fyu3r.png&h=4d267800&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wsMeeu9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwsMeeu9.png&h=38883895&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n踢波安全至上戴返個眼罩先<img src=\"/a